Author: bluediner
Text: Thank you for this! Ever since I upped my intake, I’ve actually really changed the way I look at food. Usually, I’m satisfied with just the serving size/just one of treats (especially because a lot of sugar just gives me a killer headache), but today was very overwhelming emotionally, so I kinda threw that all out the window for a brief moment.

Author: unsurebanana
Text: That's amazing! Congrats! Don't feel guilty because I've learned that this is how "naturally" skinny people eat (my roommate was one of these people), and she would buy sooo much junk and only eat a little bit once in a while.
